    <item>
      <title>哥伦比亚Threadneedle预计英镑将因利率押注上涨至1.50美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/columbia-threadneedle-sees-pound-rallying-to-1-50-on-rate-bets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哥伦比亚线程针投资公司（Columbia Threadneedle Investments）认为，由于英国放松政策的速度慢于美国，英镑将升至英国脱欧公投前的水平，这是迄今为止同类货币中最乐观的预测。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/columbia-threadneedle-sees-pound-rallying-to-1-50-on-rate-bets</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 11:02:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧元区通胀率跌破 2%，支持欧洲央行降息押注</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/euro-zone-inflation-drops-below-2-backing-ecb-rate-cut-bets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧元区通胀率自 2021 年以来首次低于欧洲央行 2% 的目标——支持了投资者押注利率可能会比之前预期的更快下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/euro-zone-inflation-drops-below-2-backing-ecb-rate-cut-bets</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员增加对欧洲央行本月降息的押注，全球债券市场上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/europe-leads-bond-rally-with-october-cut-almost-fully-priced</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着越来越多的迹象表明欧洲经济需要放松货币政策，欧洲政府债券价格上涨，交易员为欧洲更快降息做好准备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/europe-leads-bond-rally-with-october-cut-almost-fully-priced</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 08:59:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贝莱德的 Fink 表示市场对美联储降息的预测是错误的</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/blackrock-s-fink-says-market-is-wrong-to-bet-on-so-many-fed-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[贝莱德公司首席执行官拉里芬克表示，鉴于美国经济持续增长，市场对美联储降息的预期过于强烈。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/blackrock-s-fink-says-market-is-wrong-to-bet-on-so-many-fed-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 08:13:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非的 Ramokgopa 期望政府干预电价</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/s-africa-s-ramokgopa-expects-state-intervention-on-power-prices</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非政府计划采取干预措施，以降低电价，此前南非国家公用事业公司向监管机构请求将电价提高 36%。]]></description>
